7
00:00:34,020 --> 00:00:40,420
And these chats also have, some are just sequestered to large MAGA influencers in which they send these paid campaigns.

8
00:00:40,640 --> 00:00:42,260
Others have members of the administration.

9
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:48,340
Others have, you know, the Trump children and they coordinate this messaging and react to things in real time.

10
00:00:48,460 --> 00:00:53,380
Here's how we respond or don't respond to any given issue at any given time.

11
00:00:53,820 --> 00:00:57,540
They also have paid campaigns in which messaging is pushed out.

12
00:00:57,980 --> 00:01:05,740
And it is very much coordinated through both paid messaging and just wanting to be in the club and not be ostracized.

13
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:07,540
Were you in these chats yourself?

14
00:01:07,660 --> 00:01:08,300
You've seen this firsthand?

15
00:01:08,580 --> 00:01:08,840
Yes.

16
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:09,740
Yes.

17
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:11,040
Those screenshots are from me.

18
00:01:11,100 --> 00:01:11,880
I was in these chats.

19
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:14,680
And these chats are not just, you know, lower level freaks.

20
00:01:14,720 --> 00:01:17,000
These are big names of the conservative media machine.

21
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:23,000
Members of Congress, members of the administration, people at the White House, people with the last name Trump.

22
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:25,500
Would someone like a Tucker Carlson have been in there until recently?

23
00:01:26,180 --> 00:01:28,340
